###

### Get all recipes
GET localhost:3000/recipes

###

### Get recipe by id
GET localhost:3000/recipes/id_da_receita

###

### Update recipe
PUT localhost:3000/recipes/id_da_receita
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Chocolate Cake",
  "description": "Better chocolate cake"
}

###

### Delete recipe
DELETE localhost:3000/recipes/id_da_receita
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}